{"nbformat": 4, "nbformat_minor": 4, "metadata": {"kernelspec": {"display_name": "Python 3", "language": "python", "name": "python3"}, "language_info": {"name": "python", "version": "3.8.0", "mimetype": "text/x-python", "file_extension": ".py"}}, "cells": [{"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["# NL Team Trends — Seasonal Trend Analysis Notebook\n\nThis notebook provides interactive seasonal trend analysis for National League performance data.\n\n## Prerequisites\n```bash\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n## Usage\n```bash\njupyter notebook notebooks/seasonal_analysis.ipynb\n```\n\n## Data Files Used\n- `data/nl_historical_performance.csv`\n- `data/nl_all_time_records.csv`\n- `data/nl_seasonal_standings.csv`\n- `data/nl_divisional_titles.csv`\n- `data/nl_wild_card_winners.csv`\n- `data/nl_pennant_winners.csv`\n"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 1. Load Data & Libraries"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["import pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nimport seaborn as sns\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n%matplotlib inline\n\nDATA_DIR = Path(\"../data\")\n\n# Load all data\nperf = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"nl_historical_performance.csv\")\nall_time = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"nl_all_time_records.csv\")\nseasonal = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"nl_seasonal_standings.csv\")\ndiv_titles = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"nl_divisional_titles.csv\")\nwc = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"nl_wild_card_winners.csv\")\npennant = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"nl_pennant_winners.csv\")\nrecent = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"nl_recent_standings.csv\")\nh2h = pd.read_csv(DATA_DIR / \"nl_team_vs_team_summary.csv\")\n\nprint(\"Data loaded successfully!\")\nprint(f\"Historical performance records: {len(perf)} seasons\")\nprint(f\"All-time franchise records: {len(all_time)} teams\")\nprint(f\"Seasonal standings: {len(seasonal)} entries\")\nprint(f\"Divisional titles: {len(div_titles)} entries\")\nprint(f\"Wild card winners: {len(wc)} entries\")"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 2. Era Win-Rate Analysis"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["# Classify eras\nseasonal[\"Era\"] = seasonal[\"Year\"].apply(\n    lambda y: \"60G (COVID)\" if y == 2020 else \n    (\"154G Era\" if y <= 1961 else \"162G Era\")\n)\n\n# Calculate average win% by era\nev = seasonal.groupby(\"Era\")[\"Overall_WPct\"].agg([\"mean\", \"std\", \"count\"])\nprint(\"\\n=== Win% by Era ===\")\nprint(ev)\n\n# Boxplot\nplt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\nseasonal.boxplot(column=\"Overall_WPct\", by=\"Era\", grid=False)\nplt.title(\"NL Season Win% Distribution by Era\")\nplt.suptitle(\"\")\nplt.xlabel(\"Schedule Era\")\nplt.ylabel(\"Overall Win% (W/(W+L))\")\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"../charts/era_winbox.png\", dpi=150)\nplt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 3. Division Dominance Over Time"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["# Count division titles by division\nprint(\"\\n=== Division Titles by Division ===\")\nprint(div_titles[\"Division\"].value_counts())\n\n# Visualize\nplt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\ndiv_counts = div_titles[\"Division\"].value_counts()\ndiv_counts.plot(kind=\"bar\", color=[\"firebrick\", \"steelblue\", \"mediumgreen\"])\nplt.title(\"Division Title Counts by Division (1876-2025)\")\nplt.xlabel(\"Division\")\nplt.ylabel(\"Title Count\")\nplt.xticks(rotation=0)\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"../charts/division_title_counts.png\", dpi=150)\nplt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 4. Championship Drought Analysis"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["# Teams with most WS titles\ntop_ws = all_time.sort_values(\"WS_Titles\", ascending=False)\nprint(\"\\n=== NL Franchises by WS Titles ===\")\nprint(top_ws[[\"Team\", \"WS_Titles\", \"Wins\", \"Losses\", \"WinPct\"]].head(10))\n\n# Visualize\nplt.figure(figsize=(14, 8))\ncolors = [\"gold\" if x > 0 else \"lightcoral\" for x in top_ws[\"WS_Titles\"]]\nplt.barh(top_ws[\"Team\"], top_ws[\"WS_Titles\"], color=colors)\nplt.title(\"NL Franchise World Series Titles\")\nplt.xlabel(\"World Series Titles\")\nplt.gca().invert_yaxis()\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"../charts/ws_titles_drought.png\", dpi=150)\nplt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 5. Expansion Impact Analysis"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["expansion_teams = [\"Miami Marlins\", \"Colorado Rockies\", \"Arizona Diamondbacks\", \n              \"San Diego Padres\", \"Milwaukee Brewers\", \"Washington Nationals\", \n              \"New York Mets\"]\n\nexp = all_time[all_time[\"Team\"].isin(expansion_teams)].sort_values(\"WinPct\", ascending=False)\norig = all_time[~all_time[\"Team\"].isin(expansion_teams)].sort_values(\"WinPct\", ascending=False)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== Expansion Team Win% ===\")\nprint(exp[[\"Team\", \"WinPct\", \"WS_Titles\"]])\n\nprint(\"\\n=== Top 10 Original NL Franchise Win% ===\")\nprint(orig[[\"Team\", \"WinPct\", \"WS_Titles\"]].head(10))\n\nfig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(14, 6))\naxes[0].barh(exp[\"Team\"], exp[\"WinPct\"], color=\"orange\", alpha=0.8)\naxes[0].set_title(\"Expansion Team Win%\")\naxes[0].set_xlabel(\"Winning Percentage\")\naxes[0].invert_yaxis()\naxes[1].barh(orig.head(10)[\"Team\"], orig.head(10)[\"WinPct\"], color=\"steelblue\", alpha=0.8)\naxes[1].set_title(\"Top 10 Original NL Franchise Win%\")\naxes[1].set_xlabel(\"Winning Percentage\")\naxes[1].invert_yaxis()\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"../charts/expansion_impact.png\", dpi=150)\nplt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 6. H2H W-L Key Matchups"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["print(\"\\n=== Key H2H W-L Matchups ===\")\nfor _, row in h2h.iterrows():\n    t1_wins = row[\"Team_1_Wins\"]\n    t2_wins = row[\"Team_2_Wins\"]\n    total = t1_wins + t2_wins\n    if total > 0:\n        t1_pct = t1_wins/total\n        print(f\"{row['Team_1']} vs {row['Team_2']}: {t1_wins}-{t2_wins} ({t1_pct:.3f})\")\n\n# H2H Heatmap\nplt.figure(figsize=(14, 8))\nkey = h2h.head(15)\nwin_pcts = []\nfor _, row in key.iterrows():\n    t1 = row[\"Team_1_Wins\"]\n    t2 = row[\"Team_2_Wins\"]\n    total = t1 + t2\n    win_pcts.append(t1/total if total > 0 else 0.5)\n\nplt.barh(range(len(key)), win_pcts, color=\"purple\", alpha=0.8)\nplt.yticks(range(len(key)), [f\"{r['Team_1']} vs {r['Team_2']}\" for _, r in key.iterrows()])\nplt.title(\"H2H W-L Win% (Selected Matchups)\")\nplt.xlabel(\"Team_1 Win% (vs Team_2)\")\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"../charts/h2h_heatmap.png\", dpi=150)\nplt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 7. NL West Dominance (2018-2025)"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["print(\"\\n=== NL West Dominance ===\")\nprint(recent[[\"Year\", \"NL_West_W\", \"NL_West_L\"]].to_string(index=False))\n\nplt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\nplt.bar(recent[\"Year\"], recent[\"NL_West_W\"], color=\"royalblue\", alpha=0.8, label=\"NL West Wins\")\nplt.plot(recent[\"Year\"], recent[\"NL_Central_W\"], 's-', color=\"steelblue\", label=\"NL Central Wins\")\nplt.plot(recent[\"Year\"], recent[\"NL_East_W\"], 'o-', color=\"firebrick\", label=\"NL East Wins\")\nplt.title(\"NL Division Win Counts (2020-2025)\")\nplt.xlabel(\"Year\")\nplt.ylabel(\"Wins\")\nplt.legend()\nplt.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"../charts/division_win_counts_recent.png\", dpi=150)\nplt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 8. Seasonal Win% Trends (Recent Decades)"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["# Average win% by decade\ndf = seasonal.copy()\ndf[\"Decade\"] = (df[\"Year\"] // 10) * 10\ndecade_avg = df.groupby(\"Decade\")[\"Overall_WPct\"].agg([\"mean\", \"std\", \"count\"])\nprint(\"\\n=== Win% by Decade ===\")\nprint(decade_avg)\n\n# Visualize\nplt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))\nplt.bar(decade_avg.index, decade_avg[\"mean\"], color=\"teal\", alpha=0.8, width=8)\nplt.errorbar(decade_avg.index, decade_avg[\"mean\"], yerr=decade_avg[\"std\"], fmt='none', ecolor='black', capsize=3)\nplt.title(\"NL Average Win% by Decade\")\nplt.xlabel(\"Decade\")\nplt.ylabel("Average Win%\")\nplt.xticks(rotation=45)\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"../charts/decade_win_avg.png\", dpi=150)\nplt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## 9. Pennant Winners by Decade"]}, {"cell_type": "code", "execution_count": null, "metadata": {}, "source": ["pennant[\"Decade\"] = (pennant[\"Year\"] // 10) * 10\n\n# Top pennant winners all-time\nprint(\"\\n=== Pennant Winners by Franchise (All-Time) ===\")\nprint(pennant[\"Team\"].value_counts().head(10))\n\nplt.figure(figsize=(14, 8))\ntop_pennant = pennant[\"Team\"].value_counts().head(10)\ntop_pennant.plot(kind=\"bar\", color=\"purple\", alpha=0.8)\nplt.title(\"Most NL Pennant Winners by Franchise\")\nplt.xlabel(\"Team\")\nplt.ylabel(\"Pennant Titles\")\nplt.xticks(rotation=45, ha=\"right\")\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"../charts/pennant_winners_alltime.png\", dpi=150)\nplt.show()"]}, {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {}, "source": ["## Key Findings to Explore\n\n1. **Dodgers Dynasty**: 8 straight NL West titles (2018-2025) - how unprecedented is this?\n2. **Braves Dynasty**: 14 consecutive division titles (1991-2005)\n3. **Cubs Drought**: 108 years between Championships (1908-2016)\n4. **Cardinals Dominance**: 11 WS titles, most of any NL franchise\n5. **Expansion Impact**: How much have new teams affected the competitive balance?\n6. **Era Changes**: 154G → 162G → 60G - how does schedule length affect win%?\n7. **H2H Rivalries**: Dodgers-Cubs (.695), Cardinals-Cubs (.525), Dodgers-Giants (.523)\n8. **Shortened Season Comparison**: 2020 Dodgers .717 vs 2022 Dodgers .685 (162G)\n"]}]}